name: LARRY'S FOOD FIESTA (andricspaeth)
description:
Willkommen bei LARRYS FOOD FIESTA. Bitte begeben Sie sich zum Schalter um ihre Bestellung aufzugeben.

Located at  Desert LSF 50.

Enter the Desert: https://philipbaz.itch.io/larrys-food-fiesta-desert

Please use Google Chrome or Firefox to enjoy the full experience. Make sure Sound is allowed for the use of the website.
(If you're using Safari Graphics might be lacking)
